{"tid":452186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝擬爆氫彈抗美3航母集結","createTime":"2017-10-30T02:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T04:01:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25ba6901764bed222c25a1c4e612eb104794a481","tid":452186,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171030/20198954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171030%2F20198954&d=UtW9Xjt%2BaK%2Bs9a9qy0N3PpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=e6568046\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171030%2F20198954&h=fe61c1e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171030/20198954</a><br />\n<br />\n朝擬爆氫彈抗美3航母集結<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【北韓危機】<br />\n朝鮮半島戰雲密佈，美軍三大航母戰鬥群在西太平洋罕有集結，北韓官方《勞動新聞》前日撰文警告美國，稱北韓的「核力量建設大業正在處於已達到最終完成目標的階段。現在剩下的只是揚眉吐氣地顯示主體朝鮮的氣概」，呼應北韓外交官日前表明計劃在太平洋上空試爆氫彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171030/large/a1305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171030%2Flarge%2Fa1305a.gif&h=0bc3cd4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金正恩與夫人李雪主（右）視察化妝品工廠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北韓大規模疏散演習<br />\n<br />\n平壤聲稱擁核是要跟華盛頓平起平坐，但雙方核力量完全不對稱，因此口口聲聲輕視美國軍力的同時，北韓實際上卻加緊備戰，上周全國大小城鎮都舉行了全面疏散演習，規模之大是2003年以來罕見，其間又進行了所謂「停電演習」，要民眾在無燈光的情況下繼續工作，模擬戰時熄燈避免暴露位置，成為敵人攻擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普下月3日便會展開亞洲之旅訪問，白宮表明同盟友商討北韓核問題是焦點之一，北韓亞太和平委員會前日警告日本，勿在「朝核威脅論上」附和美國，否則會將日本「葬於海底」。<br />\n<br />\n朝中社/英國《每日鏡報》"},{"pid":"1c090b23f2edba329615f8cc3cca360372e972da","tid":452186,"uid":97277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"嘴炮戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519149567f71b36a7ec58381f7323cb2889faf1d","tid":452186,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗牌"}]}